dependency array.",["524"],"jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid","The href attribute is required for an anchor to be keyboard accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide an href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/evcohen/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/master/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","JSXOpeningElement","jsx-a11y/alt-text","img elements must have an alt prop, either with meaningful text, or an empty string for decorative images.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'form'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["525"],["526"],"'Select' is defined but never used.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'setUser'. Either include it or remove the dependency array. If 'setUser' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["527"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'idProduct' and 'socket'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["528"],["529"],["530"],"react/jsx-no-duplicate-props","No duplicate props allowed","JSXAttribute",["531"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'actionGetCartAPI' and 'token'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["532"],"'SubMenu' is assigned a value but never used.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'actionGetCart'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["533"],"eqeqeq","Expected '===' and instead saw '=='.","BinaryExpression","unexpected",["534"],["535"],["536"],"React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'actionGetProductId' and 'id_product'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["537"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'dataProductsEdit'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["538"],"React Hook useEffect has a complex expression in the dependency array. Extract it to a separate variable so it can